  <main>
  <section class="p-0">
    <%= render "carrossel" %>
  </section>

  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <h2 class="fw-bold mb-2">Fotos do Último ORAR</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"><%= image_tag "ulisses.jpeg", class: "img-fluid rounded shadow-sm w-100", alt: "Ulisses" %></div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"><%= image_tag "candeias.jpeg", class: "img-fluid rounded shadow-sm w-100", alt: "Candeias" %></div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"><%= image_tag "setimus.jpeg", class: "img-fluid rounded shadow-sm w-100", alt: "Setimus" %></div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"><%= image_tag "forjados.jpeg", class: "img-fluid rounded shadow-sm w-100", alt: "Forjados" %></div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"><%= image_tag "volei.jpeg", class: "img-fluid rounded shadow-sm w-100", alt: "Volei" %></div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"><%= image_tag "eldorado.jpeg", class: "img-fluid rounded shadow-sm w-100", alt: "Eldorado" %></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mt-2">
  <h2 class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center gap-2">
    <span aria-hidden="true">
      <i class="bi bi-chat-dots-fill"></i>
    </span>
    Perguntas Frequentes
  </h2>
   <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center mt-2">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card shadow-sm faq-card" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
        <div class="card-body justify-content-center">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-10 pt-3">
              <h5 class="fw-bold text-secondary">1. O que é o ORAR? 
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-2 pt-3 text-end">
              <i class="bi bi-plus-lg text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p class="text-secondary mt-2">
              As olimpíadas regionais Adventistas de Rondônia <strong>ORAR</strong> são iniciativas do ministério jovem que busca promover evolução física, mental e espiritual dos jovens. 
              O objetivo é proporcionar um ambiente saudável e estimulante para o desenvolvimento integral dos participantes, promovendo a integração entre os jovens das diferentes regiões do estado de Rondônia.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card shadow-sm faq-card" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
        <div class="card-body pt-2">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-10 pt-3">
              <h5 class="fw-bold text-secondary">3. Quando e onde vai ser o ORAR 2026?</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-2 pt-3 text-end">
              <i class="bi bi-plus-lg text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <ul class="text-secondary mt-2">
              <li>O ORAR 2026 será realizado no IFRO (Instituto Federal de Rondônia) no período de [Data Início] a [Data Fim].</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card shadow-sm faq-card" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-10 pt-3">
              <h5 class="fw-bold text-secondary">2. Quem pode participar?</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-2 pt-3 text-end">
              <i class="bi bi-plus-lg text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <ul class="text-secondary mt-2">
              <li>Todos aqueles que frequentam regulamente uma sociedade jovem</li>
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
        

<script>
  function toggleAnswer(card) {
    const answer = card.querySelector(".faq-answer");
    const icon = card.querySelector("i");
    
    answer.classList.toggle("active");

    if (answer.classList.contains("active")) {
      icon.classList.remove("bi-plus-lg");
      icon.classList.add("bi-dash-lg");
    } else {
      icon.classList.remove("bi-dash-lg");
      icon.classList.add("bi-plus-lg");
    }
  }

  function adjustFaqLayout() {
  const screenWidth = window.innerWidth;
  const faqContainers = document.querySelectorAll(".container .faq-card");

  if (screenWidth < 768) { 
    const mobileContainer = document.querySelector(".container.d-flex");
    mobileContainer.classList.remove("d-flex", "justify-content-center");

    faqContainers.forEach(card => {
      card.style.width = "100%"; 
    });
  }
}

window.addEventListener("load", adjustFaqLayout);
window.addEventListener("resize", adjustFaqLayout);

</script>


<style>
  .faq-card {
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  .faq-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0px 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .faq-answer {
    max-height: 0; 
    overflow: hidden; 
    transition: max-height 0.3s ease-out; 
  }
  .faq-answer.active {
    max-height: 200px; 
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
  .faq-card h5 {
    font-size: 1rem; 
  }

  .faq-card .row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center; 
  }

  .faq-card .col-md-10 {
    width: 85%; 
  }

  .faq-card .col-md-2 {
    width: 15%; 
    display: flex;
    align-items: center; 
    justify-content: center; 
  }

  .faq-card i {
    font-size: 1.2rem; 
  }
}
</style>
  
  </section>
</main>
